title: About
text:
About this site


Welcome to my website!
I am a Smith College senior graduating double majoring in Statistics & Data Science and Psychology. I love research in academic spaces, specifically in social science and biostatistics. I love using R

from Brookyn, New York!



Current work
I plan to go to graduate school for Biostatistics or Applied Statistics with a domain in psychology.
Currently, I am working with Dr. Amanda Almond to present research on microagressions and doctor-patient relationships at the Eastern Psychological Association

I am a Peer Advisor at the Lazarus Center for Career Development
I am a First Gen Outloud Intern
